body:
I'm hoping to use this PR to fix #10882. Couple of questions. How should we test expand? Also it seems like writing an expand_as(g, self, other) function in onnx/symbolic.py is not picked up when exporting a model containing aten::expand_as operator. I made sure that the arguments are the same as [here](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/b14f2e899c92f541644e393b2513aa60aeb9196f/aten/src/ATen/native/TensorShape.cpp#L136).

Any advice?
